<script>
export default {
  name: "RestaurantsPagination",
  props: {
    categoryId: {
      type: [String, Number],
      default: "",
    },
    currentPage: {
      type: Number,
      default: 1,
    },
    totalPage: {
      type: Array,
      required: true,
    },
    previousPage: {
      type: Number,
      required: true,
    },
    nextPage: {
      type: Number,
      required: true,
    },
  },
};
</script>
